{"tid":2415910,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"「出 duck 嚟行」<<安心出痕>>","createTime":"2021-02-20T15:19:18.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-22T03:30:34.000Z","uid":301327,"like":7,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"e32f5d978c4bdcfd9465dcb84f7cc51e9a2e288b","tid":2415910,"uid":301327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T15:19:18.000Z","msg":"香港政府目前規定市民前往政府大樓或辦事處，必須使用「安心出行」流動應用程式（LeaveHomeSafe），而政府今日（2021年2月10日）再宣布若疫情未有重大變化，會在年初七起有條件放寬食肆營業限制，包括放寬食肆晚市堂食等，但客人進入場所時須使用安心出行記錄行蹤，或登記顧客個人資料，引起網民關注。<br />\n「安心出行」變成要必須安裝，但安裝始終有疑慮! 開發小鴨幹線的HeaDuck研究所 就開發咗個「出 duck 嚟行」應用程式，還把程式開源，除了可以了解其運作，達到公開透明! 還點出&lt;&lt;安心出行&gt;&gt;的多個問題! <br />\n<a href=\"https://hk-hello-world.medium.com/安心出痕-68252f36bc44\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk-hello-world.medium.com%2F%E5%AE%89%E5%BF%83%E5%87%BA%E7%97%95-68252f36bc44&d=8a%2F9oMJQTUqWgqWpHd%2Bbkpq%2FK6ZSh20SQa5bazxoXL8%3D&h=028ca0a1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk-hello-world.medium.com/安心出痕-68252f36bc44</a><br />\n<br />\n替代方案只限於 Android, 安裝方法如下:<br />\n<br />\n* 先到 Play Store 官綱下載及安裝 APK Installer Mobile Manager<br />\n* 再到綱站 <a href=\"https://f-droid.org/en/packages\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ff-droid.org%2Fen%2Fpackages&d=8a%2F9oMJQTUqWgqWpHd%2Bbkpq%2FK6ZSh20SQa5bazxoXL8%3D&h=ba4fe9f5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://f-droid.org/en/packages</a> Find Apps 搜尋 &quot;gooutwithduck&quot; 及下載 headuck 嘅 APK<br />\n* 啟動 APK Installer Mobile Manager 然後按 Install APKs 及允許取讀<br />\n* 最後安裝 GoOutWithDuck"},{"pid":"2497fc98511b0ea762718243263b1e6a55e4e11f","tid":2415910,"uid":59832,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T15:21:26.000Z","msg":"點解唔直接f-droid install呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbf3e6995942aa599af469689fdfda1d61ebd4cc","tid":2415910,"uid":218731,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T15:21:37.000Z","msg":"啲狗而家搵緊啲假app 作者 睇路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8f8bcd042273619a1dbeeff855af5815b7be856","tid":2415910,"uid":59832,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"bbf3e6995942aa599af469689fdfda1d61ebd4cc","tid":2415910,"uid":218731,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T15:21:37.000Z","msg":"啲狗而家搵緊啲假app 作者 睇路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T15:23:00.000Z","msg":"邊個話呢個係假app<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90fb66954f9c82f6e89281575131faa878516259","tid":2415910,"uid":301327,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2497fc98511b0ea762718243263b1e6a55e4e11f","tid":2415910,"uid":59832,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T15:21:26.000Z","msg":"點解唔直接f-droid install呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T15:23:18.000Z","msg":"官綱無 f-droid"},{"pid":"d2febf995b80af438748c2aa01bed218a924042a","tid":2415910,"uid":59832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"90fb66954f9c82f6e89281575131faa878516259","tid":2415910,"uid":301327,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2497fc98511b0ea762718243263b1e6a55e4e11f","tid":2415910,"uid":59832,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T15:21:26.000Z","msg":"點解唔直接f-droid install呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T15:23:18.000Z","msg":"官綱無 f-droid"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T15:24:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9cjx6v6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9cjx6v6.png&h=bde894a7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a6bdb5369f43c9fb60dcb28868623cb7e2da6e21","tid":2415910,"uid":301327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T15:24:40.000Z","msg":"Push<br />\n推"},{"pid":"20834b52e21842282db9d0121efbb62dae60ea3a","tid"